\n        <button class=\"sfaq-btn\" type=\"button\">\n          Do I need to set up the stereo pair manually?\n          <span class=\"sfaq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"sfaq-answer\">\n          No — both speakers in the 2-pack auto-pair with each other the moment you turn them on. They split into left and right channels automatically. Just connect your phone to one speaker and both play instantly in stereo.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"sfaq-item\">\n        <button class=\"sfaq-btn\" type=\"button\">\n          How long does the battery last?\n          <span class=\"sfaq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"sfaq-answer\">\n          Each speaker runs 6+ hours at 50% volume, with 220+ hours standby time. They recharge via USB-C, and a full charge takes approximately 1–1.5 hours.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"sfaq-item\">\n        <button class=\"sfaq-btn\" type=\"button\">\n          Is it waterproof?\n          <span class=\"sfaq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"sfaq-answer\">\n          The speakers are splash-resistant for everyday use — light rain and sweaty hands are no problem. They are not rated for submersion or heavy water exposure, so avoid using them in the shower or near pools.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"sfaq-item\">\n        <button class=\"sfaq-btn\" type=\"button\">\n          Can I use just one speaker, or do I need both?\n          <span class=\"sfaq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"sfaq-answer\">\n          You can absolutely use a single speaker on its own in mono mode. The 2-pack is designed for stereo pairing, but each unit functions as a fully independent Bluetooth speaker.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"sfaq-item\">\n        <button class=\"sfaq-btn\" type=\"button\">\n          Will the vibration damage my furniture?\n          <span class=\"sfaq-icon\">+</span>\n        </button>\n        <div class=\"sfaq-answer\">\n          No. The vibration level is similar to a phone on vibrate mode — it won't scratch or damage surfaces. The included sticker pads are residue-free and safe to remove from any surface.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\ndocument.querySelectorAll('.sfaq-btn').forEach(function(btn){\n  btn.addEventListener('click', function(){\n    var item = this.closest('.sfaq-item');\n    var isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');\n    document.querySelectorAll('.sfaq-item').forEach(function(i){ i.classList.remove('open'); });\n    if(!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');\n  });\n});\n</script>",
